==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: one-horse
<hw>one"-horse`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Drawn
by one horse; having but a single horse; <as>as, a <ex>one-horse</ex>
carriage</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Second-rate; inferior; small; <as>as, a
<ex>one-horse</ex> town</as>.</def> <mark>[Slang, U.S.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Oneidas</ent>⟦br⟧
